creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
Want your paycheck early? Get your money up to 15 days early with B9*. Use your VISA® debit card anywhere. Cash out money before your paycheck with the B9 app.

B9 is an interest-free payroll advance app available for Android devices. Get cash fast, no need to borrow money to pay bills. Manage money better with a salary advance from B9.


Whether you have savings goals, want a money transfer or simply need to go shopping, bnine.com is here to help. You can use B9 to get paid up to 15 days early.*

B9 is the cash app for Android devices. Download B9 on Google Play to get a cash advance on your earnings. Receive a payroll advance with bnine.com.



💯 WHAT YOU GET WITH B9
Best app to get a ZERO fee cash advance on your wages
No-interest pay advance

💵 B9 WALLET
$4.99/month account fees
No minimum balance required
Transfer money for free between B9 members

💳 VISA® DEBIT CARD
Use your VISA® debit card anywhere at no cost
$0 ATM fees for withdrawals*

🔒 SAFE AND SECURE TRANSACTIONS
FDIC insured account funds
Encrypted data protection for secure money transfers

☎️ CUSTOMER SUPPORT
Need help? Our B9 support team is ready to assist you
¡Hablamos español! We speak your native language

✅ OUR TOP FEATURES:
- Fee-free salary advance up to 100% of your income
-Send money to friends & family
-Manage your money
-No credit check
-Online check cashing - coming soon
-International money transfers - coming soon

PRICING & TERMS:

B9 offers an auto-renewing monthly subscription is $4.99/month.

Banking Services are provided by BAAS Corporation banking partner, Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. B9 Account℠ is provided by, and B9 Visa® Card, issued by Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. B9 Account is a service mark of B9, Inc., which offers demand deposit account among its suite of financial products and services. Visa® is a registered trademark, and the circles design is a trademark of Visa® International. B9 Account is FDIC Insured.

B9 Advance℠ is an optional, no fee service offered by B9 to its members that requires $500 in qualifying direct deposits to the B9 Account℠ each month. The amount of advance pay you are eligible to receive will be based on member's B9 Account℠ history, direct deposit frequency and amount, spending activity and other risk-based factors and criteria determined by B9, and may change from time to time. You will be informed of your current available amount in the B9 mobile app. You will receive notice of any changes to your limit. Your limit may change at any time, at B9's discretion. See Terms of Services and contact B9 via support@bnine.com for additional terms, conditions and eligibility requirements. May not be available in all states.

B9 warrants that it has no legal or contractual claim against you based on a failure to repay an advance, but B9 will not provide you further advances while any amount remains unpaid under the B9 Advance℠ service. With respect to a failure to repay an advance, B9 warrants it will not engage in any debt collection activities, place the amount owed with or sell to a third party, or report you to a consumer reporting agency.

The B9 Visa® Card can be used for no-fee withdrawals at ATMs in the Allpoint network. Fees may apply for ATM transactions outside this network.

“B9 is really patient when you have unexpected emergencies with paying back and they will work with you on your repayment date for the advance. Matteo

“Finally found a bank that’s not so complicated, looking forward to getting my debit card in the mail!”
Tiara

Dee

title: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
B9 is an no-interest payroll advance app available for Android devices. Get cash fast, no need to borrow money to pay bills. Manage money better with a paycheck advance from B9.

No credit check, no fee & interest salary advances of up to 100% of your wages.

👩🏾‍⚕️ HOW B9 PAYCHECK ADVANCE WORKS
• Start depositing your paycheck into your B9 account
• Confirm the B9 Advance amount you’re eligible for - this is your limit
• Take out the money (up to your limit) you need — whenever you need it
• On your actual payday, your account will be debited the amount of money you advanced - with no interest!
• The more on-time payments you make, the more of your income we can advance to you over time — up to 100%

💵 DIGITAL WALLET
$9.99/month account fees
● No minimum balance needed
● NO fee money transfers between B9 members.

💳 NO Fee VISA® DEBIT CARD
● Use it anywhere!

🔒 SAFE AND SECURE TRANSACTIONS
● FDIC insured account funds
● Encrypted data protection for secure money transfers

☎️ AWARD-WINNING CUSTOMER SUPPORT
● Need help? Our B9 support team is ready to assist you

🇪🇸 ¡HABLAMOS ESPANOL!
● …and many more languages

💯 MORE FEATURES OF B9 CASH ADVANCE
• No-Fee salary advance of up to 100% of your income
• Bilingual helpful customer service
• Low monthly fee
• No limit cash earning referral program


❤️ WHAT OUR CUSTOMERS SAY

“B9 is really patient when you have unexpected emergencies with paying back and they will work with you on your repayment date for the advance. They have great customer service and I really like my account with them. I would recommend possibly adding a savings account to the app so we can have a full-fledged bank account.”
Matteo

“Finally found a bank that’s not so complicated, looking forward to getting my debit card in the mail!”
Tiara

“I recently switched to B9 to transfer money easier between my family and it's been a great experience. Their customer service is so fast, most of my family members only speak Spanish and they were also able to have all their questions answered quickly!”
Dee

✅ DOWNLOAD B9 IF:
-You applied for help but got denied even though you get a paycheck every month.

-You’re doing your best to spend less - but your month-to-month expenses are still more than you bargained for.

-After all your careful planning and sacrifices, you’re still living paycheck-to-paycheck.
-The prices of things have gone up, but it’s been a while since you’ve gotten a new promotion, raise, or bonus.
-It’s almost time to pay your rent, car, or electricity bill

For more information, please visit bnine.com

B9 is not a bank. Banking Services are provided by Mbanq banking partner, Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. B9 Account℠ is provided by, and B9 Visa® Card, is issued by Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. B9 Account℠ is a service mark of B9, Inc., which offers demand deposit account among its suite of financial products and services. Visa® is a registered trademark of Visa® International. B9 Account℠ is FDIC Insured.
B9 Advance℠ is an optional, no fee service offered by B9 to its members that requires to set up a payroll direct deposits to the B9 Account℠ each month. The amount of advance a member is eligible to get earlier will be based on member's B9 Account℠ history, payroll direct deposit frequency and amount, and other factors determined by B9, and may change from time to time. If a member directs funds to its B9 Account℠ outside his/her paycheck, those funds will not count towards payroll deposit.

title: B9 - Paycheck Early & CashBack

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
B9 can provide up to $500 in cash advances with no credit check and no interest. Get your paycheck early so you
can pay bills, get cash, or transfer money!
---
HOW IT WORKS
---
1. Start depositing your paycheck into your B9 account (we’ll show you how in a few easy steps):
2. Confirm the B9 Advance amount you’re eligible for. This is your limit.
3. Take out the money (up to your limit) you need—whenever you need it.
4. On your actual payday, your account will be debited the amount of money you advanced- with NO
INTEREST!
5. The more on-time payments you make, the more of your income we can advance to you over time — up to
100%!
—
WHAT YOU GET WITH B9
---
NO CREDIT CHECK, NO FEE & NO INTEREST salary advances
Up to 100% of your earnings
REVOLUTIONARY PLANS
Basic Plan ($9.99/month)
B9 Visa® Debit Card with 4% Cashback
No-Fee B9 Advances (up to $300)
No-Fee Instant Transfers to B9 Members
Get advances instantly
Premium plan ($19.99/month)
All the features in the Basic plan PLUS:
B9 Advance of up to 100% of your paycheck*
Credit Report
Credit Score
Credit Score Simulator
UP TO 4% CASHBACK
The ONLY debit card that offers an accumulation of cashback every time you use your B9 Visa® Debit Card for fast
food, gas, or restaurants.
We will automatically match all the cashback you've earned during the year- dollar for dollar!
SAFE AND SECURE TRANSACTIONS
Funds are FDIC insured up to $250,000 through Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC
Encrypted data protection for secure transfers
AWARD-WINNING CUSTOMER SUPPORT
Need help? Our B9 support team is ready to assist you
¡HABLAMOS ESPANOL!
...and many more languages
—
MORE B9 FEATURES
—
No hidden fees
No limit cash earning referral program
---
DOWNLOAD B9 IF:
—
-You applied for a loan but got denied even though you get a paycheck every month
-You’ve looked into pay-day loans but didn’t want the high-interest rates
-You’re doing your best to spend less — but your month-to-month expenses are still more than you bargained for
-After all your careful planning and sacrifices, you’re still living paycheck-to-paycheck
-The prices of things have gone up, but it’s been a while since you’ve gotten a new promotion, raise, or bonus
-It’s almost time to pay your rent, car loan, or electricity bill
---
ABOUT US:
—
-Meet B9, the new revolution in fintech banking that gives you access to up to 100% of your paycheck 15 days
early, NO-INTEREST!
-And THE ONLY fintech banking app truly designed to support your job, your home, your health, your leisure, your
family—your money.
—
REAL USER REVIEWS
—
“Finally found an app that’s not as complicated as traditional banking, looking forward to getting my debit card in
the mail!”
Tiara
“I recently switched to B9 to transfer money easier between my family and it's been a great experience. Their
customer service is so fast, most of my family members only speak Spanish and they were also able to have all
their questions answered quickly!”
Dee Leonie
For more information, please visit bnine.com

B9 Account℠ is a service mark of B9, Inc., which offers demand deposit account among its suite of financial products and services.
Visa® is a registered trademark of Visa® International. B9 Account℠ is FDIC Insured.
B9 Advance℠ and B9 Premium℠ are optional services, offered by B9 to its members that require to set up a payroll
direct deposits to the B9 Account each month. All B9 Advance℠ and B9 Premium℠ members start with up to $100
early pay advance. B9 Premium℠ members have the potential for it to increase up to 100% of their earnings they
deposit from their paycheck to their B9 Account. All B9 members are informed of their current available maxes in
the B9 mobile app. Their limit may change at any time, at B9's discretion.

title: B9 Cash Advance Early Paycheck

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
When you need cash right now! Get paycheck advance, cash advance & money now! B9 can provide up to $500 in an instant, quick, fast and same day cash advance no credit check — 15 days early — with NO INTEREST. Plus, 5% cash back with your B9 Visa debit card — the ONLY debit card that offers that! A credit card cash advance won't directly hurt your credit score.

Just your money, in your hands!
Get early paycheck advance app so you can pay bills on the same day that the receipts come, manage your earnings, get instant cash, or transfer money! Mobile banking app enable you to easily perform of your banking functions, like paying your bills the same day your receipts arrive, or accessing super-fast transfers through the ACH network (representing over 10,000 financial institutions!). Payday app is your cash assistant!

How it works:
Start depositing your paycheck early into your B9 Account:
1) Confirm the B9 Early Paycheck Advance amount you’re eligible for — that’ll be your limit.
2) Take out the money you need (up to your limit).
3) On the actual payday, your account will be debited the amount of money you stated.
4) The more on-time payments you make, the more of your income we can prepay you — up to 100% of your paycheck!


Why B9?
We started B9 to serve hardworking Americans typically ignored by the banking industry. Here’s where we’re different: we don’t care about your credit history — just your income. If you’re making money we’re good to get you what’s yours. Getting your paycheck early could help you cover life’s sudden expenses without taking on debt.

Plans:
Basic ($9.99/month)
No-Fee B9 Advances (up to $300).
B9 Visa Debit Card with up to 5% Cashback.
No-Fee Instant Transfers to B9 Members.
Same Day Instant Pay.

Premium ($19.99/month)
Everything in Basic PLUS:
Up to 100% of your paycheck.
Credit Report & Score (Typically costing around $15 for a one-time credit report and score from a single credit bureau, or $30-$40 for reports and scores from all three).
Credit Score Simulator (lets you explore how changes on your credit report could affect your score).

Download B9 if you:
Applied for a loan but got denied even though you get a paycheck every month.
Looked into pay day loans but didn’t want the high-interest rates.
Did your best to spend less but your month-to-month expenses are still more.
Continue to live paycheck to paycheck — despite all your careful planning and sacrifices.

Universal:
FDIC insured up to $250,000 through Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. Among its partners: Branch, Deserve, Mastercard, Visa, and other finance & banking apps.
Encrypted data protection for secure transfers in the finance app.
Fast, award-winning customer support.
¡HABLAMOS ESPAÑOL! and many more languages.

Financial & Credit technologies has made it easier than ever to borrow money quickly. A cash advance is one of the easiest ways to get paid early. Getting a payday advance might only be a few taps away.

Payday loan app, or payday advance app, provide a short-term loan. When you need cash to make it to payday, these service can be a huge help. You can also get up to $500 with a same-day instant cash advance.

title: B9 Cash Advance Early Paycheck

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
When you need cash right now! Get paycheck advance, cash advance & money now! B9 can provide up to $500 in an instant, quick, fast and same day cash advance no credit check — 15 days early — with NO INTEREST. Plus, 5% cash back with your B9 Visa debit card — the ONLY debit card that offers that! A credit card cash advance won't directly hurt your credit score.

Just your money, in your hands!
Get early paycheck advance app so you can pay bills on the same day that the receipts come, manage your earnings, get instant cash, or transfer money! Mobile banking app enable you to easily perform of your banking functions, like paying your bills the same day your receipts arrive, or accessing super-fast transfers through the ACH network (representing over 10,000 financial institutions!). Payday app is your cash assistant!

How it works:
Start depositing your paycheck early into your B9 Account:
1) Confirm the B9 Early Paycheck Advance amount you’re eligible for — that’ll be your limit.
2) Take out the money you need (up to your limit).
3) On the actual payday, your account will be debited the amount of money you stated.
4) The more on-time payments you make, the more of your income we can prepay you — up to 100% of your paycheck!


Why B9?
We started B9 to serve hardworking Americans typically ignored by the banking industry. Here’s where we’re different: we don’t care about your credit history — just your income. If you’re making money we’re good to get you what’s yours. Getting your paycheck early could help you cover life’s sudden expenses without taking on debt.

Plans:
Basic ($9.99/month)
No-Fee B9 Advances (up to $300).
B9 Visa Debit Card with up to 5% Cashback.
No-Fee Instant Transfers to B9 Members.
Same Day Instant Pay.

Premium ($19.99/month)
Everything in Basic PLUS:
Up to 100% of your paycheck.
Credit Report & Score (Typically costing around $15 for a one-time credit report and score from a single credit bureau, or $30-$40 for reports and scores from all three).
Credit Score Simulator (lets you explore how changes on your credit report could affect your score).

Download B9 if you:
Applied for a loan but got denied even though you get a paycheck every month.
Looked into pay day loans but didn’t want the high-interest rates.
Did your best to spend less but your month-to-month expenses are still more.
Continue to live paycheck to paycheck — despite all your careful planning and sacrifices.

Universal:
FDIC insured up to $250,000 through Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. Among its partners: Branch, Deserve, Mastercard, Visa, and other finance & banking apps.
Encrypted data protection for secure transfers in the finance app.
Fast, award-winning customer support.
¡HABLAMOS ESPAÑOL! and many more languages.

Member Talk
“It’s been a game-changer in regards to me keeping all my gig work income in order — their B9 Cash Advance feature helps me a lot when I've been a little short."
Juan L, Amazon Flex Driver

“Didnt’ have to do too much. Didn’t have to discuss anything with anybody. Just had to type in my credentials in Cash Advance app.”
Courtney P, app user

“I do try to tell people about it whenever I hear people asking about a better way of banking. And I tell them, this little card I have here, the B9 Cash Advance card, it actually helps.”
Christopher R, car driver

“Where is the cash store? Here is he! I have many good cash apps: Empower, Chime and Rise Credit. But most often I use B9 Cash Advance. It is convenient and reliable, like other apps.”
Tony M, financial business writer

No need to go to the bank for a loan!
Financial & Credit technologies has made it easier than ever to borrow money quickly. A cash advance is one of the easiest ways to get paid early. Getting a payday advance might only be a few taps away.

Payday loan app, or payday advance app, provide a short-term loan. When you need cash to make it to payday, these service can be a huge help. You can also get up to $500 with a same-day instant cash advance.

B9 Basic ($9.99/mo)

B9 Premium (19.99/mo)
B9 Basic plus before payday advances up to $500 cash, credit reports, score checker, and simulator, plus fast, premium customer support.

How B9 Advance Works
1.Start your pay advance by putting your paycheck early into your B9 account (from the B9 advance app).
2.Confirm your early paycheck advance—the max amount of an early paycheck available for instant cash transfers before payday. Make paycheck deposit receipts of at least $600 a month. Pay your advances back by the day they’re due. Early paycheck advances start as low as $30 but can go to $500 depending on which B9 payday advance plan you choose. On payday—after the money is in your account—the $ advanced will be debited.
3.Get your cash advance early, before payday

5% Cashback
Choose 4 categories a month from a list in your B9 payday advance app, then spend more than $200 within the categories. Your cashback will be deposited into your account the 5th of the following month. Check transfers and receipts from the app.

Secure
B9 is a FinTech, not a bank and FDIC insured up to $250K thru Evolve Bank & Trust. We use PCI-DSS to encrypt all your info.

If a member directs funds to its B9 Account℠ outside his/her paycheck, those funds will not count towards their payroll deposit. See Terms of Services or contact B9 via support@bnine.com. Pay it back when you can. Set the terms in-app or reach out to support@bnine.com

How B9 Advance Works

3. Get your cash advance early, before payday

5% Cashback

Secure

title:
B9 - Earn up to 5% cashback
1.0.13

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
Tired of waiting your next payday? Access your paycheck and get paid when you need to. B9 enables you to advance your cash as you work, eliminating the wait time of your next payday. No interest, no credit checks, and no late fees. Over 1.5 million downloads and counting. Experience the B9 cash advance where you can access up to $500 per pay period to handle your unexpected bills, expenses, and so on.[1] What's more, our credit monitoring feature is included in the B9 Premium Plan, ensuring your credit goals stay on track, all conveniently within the app.

Earn up to 5% cash back when you use your B9 Visa® Debit Card for eligible purchases online and in physical stores.
Subject to eligibility criteria including spending requirements of $200 in a single calendar month and merchant categories. See T&C for more details

HOW IT WORKS:

1 Download the app and open your B9 account; start depositing your income or paycheck into your B9 account. (Any recurring direct deposits from multiple employers, side hustles, government benefits, income from rentals, tutoring also qualify.)
2 Check the amount of B9 cash advance you're eligible for, and confirm it for immediate use as you wish.
3 Withdraw or spend your cash advance money — whenever you need it.
4 When your next paycheck deposit comes, your B9 account will be debited with the amount of cash advanced.
5 The more on-time payments you make, the more of your income we can advance to you over time.

Choose your subscription plan:

Basic Plan ($11.99 or $0* monthly fee)

- B9 Visa® Debit Card with up to 5% cash back
- B9 cash advance (up to $100 cash advance per pay period) [1]
- Cash advance is available instantly with your B9 Visa® Debit Card
- No fee ACH withdrawals to banks accounts
- Additional fees apply for instant withdrawals and deposits from and to B9 account
- Instant transfers to other B9 members from your B9 account at no extra fees

Premium Plan ($19.99 or $0* monthly fee)

- B9 Visa® Debit Card with up to 5% cash back
- B9 Advance℠ (up to $500 of cash advance per pay period) [1]
- Cash advance is available instantly with your B9 Visa® Debit Card
- Instant transfers to other B9 members from your B9 account at no extra fees
- No fee ACH withdrawals to banks accounts
- Additional fees apply for instant withdrawals and deposits from and to B9 Account
- No-impact Credit Report
- Credit Score Simulator


*We'll waive the subscription fee for your first 30 days of B9 Basic. After that, it's $11.99 a month for Basic or $19.99 for Premium. If you direct-deposit more than $5K/month you'll continue to get your B9 subscription fee free. This does not exempt other fees see bnine.com/tos

B9 is not a bank. Banking Services are provided by Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC. The B9 account and B9 Visa® Card are provided by Evolve Bank & Trust, Member FDIC.

[1] B9 advance is an optional, no fee service offered by B9 to its members that requires members to set up a direct deposit to your B9 account at least once each month. The amount of cash advance a member is eligible to receive will be based on the member's B9 account history, income deposit frequency and amount, and other factors determined by B9, and may change from time to time. For B9 advance T&C and eligibility requirements apply. Not all users will qualify. Advances amounts range from $30 to $500 per pay period. Average approved cash advance in B9 Basic plan is $79 and the average approved cash advance in the B9 Premium plan is $257 as of April 2024. See T&C or contact B9 via support@bnine.com. May not be available in all states. B9 warrants that it has no legal or contractual claim against you based on a failure to repay a cash advance. B9 will not provide a customer with further advances while any amount their prior B9 advance remains unpaid under the B9 advance service.

title:
B9: Fast Cash Advance
3.4.0

creator: B9 - Get Your Paycheck Early
descriptionHtml:
Need Money Before Payday? Get Paid Early with B9!

Tired of waiting for payday? Want a banking app that helps you access your paycheck early, earn rewards, and even make extra cash? B9 gives you early access to your earnings, everyday banking tools, and new ways to earn money right from your phone — no credit checks, no interest, no late fees.
Over 1.5 million users already trust B9 to make their money work harder.

Receive your initial $50 cash advance after your first qualified paycheck direct deposit of $300+ and successful debit card link. Terms apply.

Why Choose B9 App?

- Cash Advances Up to $750 per Pay Period — Why wait for payday when life doesn’t wait for you? Get early access to your paycheck and enjoy what matters most.
- Everyday Mobile Banking — Open your B9 Account in minutes, move funds your way with ACH, Wire, or fast card transfers, and enjoy both virtual and plastic B9 Visa® Debit Cards—all with no overdraft fees or minimum balance.
- Make Extra Money in the App — Want to turn your free time into cash? Earn money by completing simple tasks like games and app downloads right inside B9.
- Personal Loans (California residents only) — Planning something bigger and need more than your B9 Advance? Use B9 regularly and you could become eligible for a B9 Personal Loan offer.
- Earn Up to 5% Cashback — Earn up to 5% cashback when you use your B9 Visa® Debit Card for daily purchases.
